OL,15,     Ginterviews with colleagues and
OL,16,     Gfriends and extracts from her
OL,17,     Gballets.
OL,18,G0200FArt That Made Us
OL,19,     GThe savagery of the world wars
OL,20,     Gchanges British art forever.
